WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.266 --> 00:00:01.266
Do you have a betrothal agreement with Consort Rong?

2
00:00:01.600 --> 00:00:02.766
No, Your Majesty.

3
00:00:03.166 --> 00:00:05.066
You and Consort Rong were childhood sweethearts.

4
00:00:05.866 --> 00:00:08.500
Is it true or not?

5
00:00:08.766 --> 00:00:10.666
Not quite childhood sweethearts.

6
00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:12.366
When I was 8 years old, I did receive education from the grand tutor.

7
00:00:12.366 --> 00:00:15.000
But an 8-year-old child understands nothing.

8
00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:16.666
I remember that the Dragon Consort was

9
00:00:16.866 --> 00:00:19.500
Two years younger than me.

10
00:00:19.500 --> 00:00:20.966
One was 8 and the other 6.

11
00:00:21.733 --> 00:00:23.800
Both were still children.

12
00:00:23.800 --> 00:00:25.433
How could they understand?

13
00:00:25.666 --> 00:00:27.166
Thank you, Empress Dowager, for your understanding.

14
00:00:30.366 --> 00:00:33.100
I can’t believe I made him cry.

15
00:00:33.600 --> 00:00:36.666
Even when he was punished by the Empress Dowager in a past life,

16
00:00:37.066 --> 00:00:38.966
I have never seen him cry.

17
00:00:38.966 --> 00:00:41.500
Your Majesty, don’t listen to his one-sided story.

18
00:00:42.466 --> 00:00:44.200
This is what my mother heard.

19
00:00:44.200 --> 00:00:45.300
This young lady,

20
00:00:45.533 --> 00:00:48.233
Why are you slandering Shen and Consort Rong?

21
00:00:48.400 --> 00:00:51.800
Shen has never been betrothed to anyone.

22
00:00:52.000 --> 00:00:52.966
Impossible.

23
00:00:53.500 --> 00:00:54.366
Your Majesty,

24
00:00:54.933 --> 00:00:56.433
What’s happening?

25
00:00:57.166 --> 00:00:59.966
Take this person outside and beat him.

26
00:01:02.300 --> 00:01:04.233
Go on, Your Majesty.

27
00:01:04.366 --> 00:01:05.233
Empress.

28
00:01:05.400 --> 00:01:07.566
Empress, save me, Empress.

29
00:01:08.133 --> 00:01:09.000
Empress.

30
00:01:09.566 --> 00:01:11.166
He is one of your people.

31
00:01:13.933 --> 00:01:14.966
Consort Rong’s sister?

32
00:01:14.966 --> 00:01:16.366
How could I possibly know her?

33
00:01:16.366 --> 00:01:18.100
But he asked you to save him.

34
00:01:18.300 --> 00:01:19.866
I don’t know.

35
00:01:20.133 --> 00:01:21.866
Perhaps someone is inciting him

36
00:01:22.733 --> 00:01:24.000
To slander me.

37
00:01:24.000 --> 00:01:26.666
Hmph, the father of innocence.

38
00:01:26.900 --> 00:01:29.766
Once I have cleared up the matter with Prince Duan,

39
00:01:29.766 --> 00:01:31.600
You will be the first to face justice.

40
00:01:31.900 --> 00:01:33.300
No good deed goes unpunished.

41
00:01:34.100 --> 00:01:37.233
To Concubine Yan, I will return a great gift.

42
00:01:38.600 --> 00:01:39.700
Your Majesty,

43
00:01:39.733 --> 00:01:41.000
Empress Dowager,

44
00:01:41.466 --> 00:01:42.800
I have something to report.

45
00:01:42.800 --> 00:01:44.600
The true murderer of Lady Zhou

46
00:01:45.500 --> 00:01:48.100
Is the eunuch Ruofeng by Concubine Yan’s side.
